            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="314dp"
            android:text="Government Polytechnic Dhule was established in the year 1960. The campus of the institute is spread across the 52 acres of land with academic and administrative building, Workshop, Girls Hostels, Boys Hostels, Faculty and staff quarters, Play Ground and Multi-Purpose Hall with Guest House.
